room_title: Escape room "Lucky Duck Speakeasy" by Great Lakes Escape Game in Flint
room_description: Travel back in time to 1925 where American prohibition is in full swing. You find yourself inside the Lucky Ducky Speakeasy as you lead a crackdown on illegal liquor sales. Unfortunately, a bomb inside the speakeasy is set to go off in 60 minutes, destroying the building and its secrets. Can you find the evidence to identify the kingpin and bring him to justice before the clock runs out?
